reviewText: There is nothing negative that can be said about this excellent concert.  They are at their best and mind blowing harmony.

The Stylistics picture showed Russell Thomkins Jr. The DVD came with the "other" Stylistics! I will never buy this again, and will inform others about the Picture of the "Stylistics" you think is coming in the Mail ! I wanted the Stylistics with "Russell Thomkins Jr, because thats what the Picture is showing! Please do not Ripped anyone else off ! They buy what they see!

  Sincerely,
  Dr. Najinya A. Shinskia M.D.
